Alright guys, here it comes:

For those who have their TAO stored in their PolkadotJS wallet and want to stake!

Go to the following URL, by double checking that it’s indeed the official Polkadot JS website, and that the RPC is the official one from Bittensor:

https://polkadot.js.org/apps/?rpc=wss://entrypoint-finney.opentensor.ai:443#/extrinsics

You should then be on a page where you need to select 2 things:
- `Submit the following extrinsic` set that to `subtensorModule`
- The command on the right of the previous element: set that to `addStake(hotkey, amountStaked)`

Now you need to insert the hotkey of your delegate in the “hotkey” field, and the amount you want to stake, *multiplied by 1 000 000 000*, in the `amountStaked` field.
So if you want to stake 10 TAO, you need to write 10000000000.

You can find hotkeys in the community Discord, on Twitter, ...

Finally, click on “Submit transaction”.
